### Create Blog Post
POST {{host}}/api/v1/blogposts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Blog Post",
  "body": "This is the content of my first blog post using MongoDB with embedded comments.",
  "comments": [
    {
      "author": "John Doe",
      "content": "Great first post!"
    },
    {
      "author": "Jane Smith", 
      "content": "Looking forward to more content."
    }
  ]
}

### Get All Blog Posts
GET {{host}}/api/v1/blogposts

### Get Blog Post by ID (replace with actual ID from create response)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/blogposts/674f8a1b2f4d123456789abc

### Update Blog Post (replace with actual ID)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/blogposts/674f8a1b2f4d123456789abc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Blog Post Title",
  "body": "This is the updated content with new embedded comments.",
  "comments": [
    {
      "author": "John Doe",
      "content": "Great updated post!"
    },
    {
      "author": "Jane Smith", 
      "content": "The updates look good."
    },
    {
      "author": "Bob Wilson",
      "content": "New comment on updated post."
    }
  ]
}

### Delete Blog Post (replace with actual ID)
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/blogposts/674f8a1b2f4d123456789abc

### Variable for local development
@host = https://localhost:7089
